                  <TextRun>
                    <Value> High School students have the highest addiction score (5.64). Female students use social media slightly more (6.60 hrs vs 6.46 hrs for males). Nearly 1 in 3 students falls in the "High Addiction" category (score 7-10).</Value>
                    <Style>
                      <FontStyle>Normal</FontStyle>
                      <FontFamily>Arial</FontFamily>
                      <TextDecoration>None</TextDecoration>
                      <Color>DarkBlue</Color>
                    </Style>
                  </TextRun>
